<topic xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsccv1p1/imsdt_v1p1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsccv1p1/imsdt_v1p1  http://www.imsglobal.org/profile/cc/ccv1p1/ccv1p1_imsdt_v1p1.xsd">
  <title>Assignments 1 &amp; 2 Deadline and Submission Requirements</title>
  <text texttype="text/html">&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;Dear Students,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;Please note the following submission requirements for Assignments 1 &amp;amp; 2:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deadline:&lt;/strong&gt; Tuesday, January 27th&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3"&gt;
&lt;li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"&gt;Late submissions will incur a penalty of -5% per day&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;File Submission Standards:&lt;/strong&gt; Several students have submitted files that do not meet quality standards. Moving forward:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3"&gt;
&lt;li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maximum file size: 30MB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PDF format is strongly recommended&lt;/strong&gt; over PNG for optimal resolution and file size&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Points will be deducted for submissions that are blurry, illegible, image is cut off or exceed the file size limit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;Before submitting, verify that:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3"&gt;
&lt;li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"&gt;Your file is under 30MB&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"&gt;Text and images are clear and readable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"&gt;You are using PDF format when possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;This is a professional standard. Ensure your work can be properly reviewed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"&gt;Thanks,&lt;br&gt;Nina&lt;/p&gt;</text>
</topic>
